name: Butterstuff
description: Butterstuff is a new, mouth-watering hybrid weed strain made for the modern connoisseur. This cross of Velvet Glove and Peanut Butter Breath bred by TeamingWithTerps is part of their “Butter line” to combine the best of classic flavors for a new generation of tastes. Butterstuff has gorgeous, multicolored buds of dark purple, bright green and silvery calyxes that emit a layered aroma of earthy, nutty, diesel and funk notes.
